abstract: >-
  The SAGE (Synthetic Adaptive Generation Engine) provides a formal 
  mathematical framework for calculating the Sage Bound— the point where 
  decoherence outpaces correction in multi-node quantum relays. It maps 
  philosophical identity persistence to a deterministic linear program.
